                 </h1>
                 <p className="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                   Millions of users now search using ChatGPT and Gemini. Audit your <span className="text-indigo-400 font-semibold">Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)</span> instantly.
                 </p>
               </div>
               <BusinessForm onSubmit={handleAnalysis} isLoading={state.loading} />
